                "response": "Now let me assess the prospect profile. I have good data on Databricks:\n\n**Key Findings:**\n\n1. **GitHub Presence**: Strong. 340 public repos with Python (58%), Scala (18%), Go (10%) focus.\n\n2. **MLflow**: Their flagship project with 18,900 stars—a model registry and experiment tracking system. This is **directly competitive or complementary** to your product.\n\n3. **Tech Stack**: Heavy ML/data engineering (Python, Scala, Go). Perfect fit for an MLOps prospect.\n\n4. **Contact Identified**: Ali Ghodsi (Co-founder & CEO), though ideally we'd want VP Engineering or MLflow team leads.\n\n5. **Prospect Quality**: \n   - **Strong alignment**: Databricks is a data & AI platform with large ML customer base\n   - **Primary consideration**: They already own MLflow—one of the market's leading open-source model registries\n   - **Risk**: Your product may be seen as redundant to MLflow rather than complementary (depends on positioning)\n   - **Opportunity**: If your product adds value MLflow lacks (lineage depth, governance, etc.), Databricks ML platform teams might adopt internally or resell\n\n6. **Reachability**: Ali Ghodsi is a prominent founder; getting past him directly would be difficult. You'd want to research VP of Engineering or the MLflow product team instead.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"target_company\": \"Databricks\",\n  \"github_org\": \"databricks\",\n  \"tech_stack\": [\"Python\", \"Scala\", \"Go\", \"TypeScript\"],\n  \"top_repos\": [\n    { \"name\": \"mlflow\", \"stars\": 18900, \"language\": \"Python\" },\n    { \"name\": \"koalas\", \"stars\": 3400, \"language\": \"Python\" },\n    { \"name\": \"terraform-provider-databricks\", \"stars\": 490, \"language\": \"Go\" },\n    { \"name\": \"dbx\", \"stars\": 440, \"language\": \"Python\" },\n    { \"name\": \"databricks-cli\", \"stars\": 420, \"language\": \"Python\" }\n  ],\n  \"contacts\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Ali Ghodsi\", \"role\": \"Co-founder & CEO\", \"linkedin_slug\": \"alighodsi\" }\n  ],\n  \"tech_stack_overlap_pct\": 85,\n  \"fit_score\": 62,\n  \"rationale\": \"Databricks is a data-heavy ML platform company with strong technical alignment, but they own MLflow—a market-leading open-source model registry that directly overlaps your product space. Fit depends on whether your lineage-tracking differentiates from MLflow; if so, their internal ML platform teams and customers are a strong target. Reachability is moderate: you'd want to route through VP Engineering or MLflow product leadership rather than the CEO.\"\n}\n```",
